	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I think tepples suggested copying the Dendy's idea of adding more dead scanlines before VBlank as a way of helping with slowdown without resorting to overclocking. But to prevent pitch and audio problems you'd want to disable APU updates during this free cpu catch up time.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


